data.title: Big Band Birthdays - November 18: Johnny Mercer
data.meta_description:
In this Podcast Extra of "The Big Band and Swing Podcast" we celebrate the birthday of a very good vocalist.  But, he is most know for his work as a prolific and successful songwriter - Johnny Mercer.  Mercer was born November 18, 1909 in Savannah, Georgia.
* All music in this podcast are Creative Commons.  Artists are credited within the podcast.
